I have managed to get the SCO binary working under Linux using the 
IBCS emulator which is currently in alpha 
(tsx-11.mit.edu:/pub/linux/ALPHA/ibcs2). 

You need a fairly modern kernel to do this (I'm using 1.0.5, but 1.0 is
also OK).

If you want more information on this, drop me a note.

Mark
